{"tid":1436361,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中共外交部：美國國務院顛倒黑白，請停止干預香港","createTime":"2019-08-09T09:31:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-09T12:56:06.000Z","uid":134071,"like":5,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"646c637a20244d06806997c2ea9e2ff16cba529a","tid":1436361,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T09:31:54.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?csid=261_367&amp;itemid=1150880&amp;PageSpeed=noscript\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3Fcsid%3D261_367%26itemid%3D1150880%26PageSpeed%3Dnoscript&d=mdS8n1K3gC4RK9SJ0KjOq%2FSletu%2BpyBbwtETYsduqsw%3D&h=3f4b505c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?csid=261_367&amp;itemid=1150880&amp;PageSpeed=noscript</a><br />\n<br />\n外交部批美國國務院發言人顛倒黑白倒打一耙<br />\n09.08.2019 16:46<br />\n<br />\n美國國務院發言人奧塔格斯批評中方，洩露美國駐港總領事館女外交官個人資料，是野蠻政權的行徑，在北京，外交部發言人華春瑩回應指，美方頻頻插手香港事務，必然引起中國人民堅決反對及強烈憤慨，美國國務院發言人首先應反思自身的言行，不應拿媒體報道說事，借此攻擊別國政府，更是顛倒黑白、倒打一耙，企圖掩蓋美方干涉中國內政的事實。<br />\n<br />\n華春瑩強調，香港是中國的香港，中國的民心不可辱、民意不可欺，敦促美方遵守國際法及國際關係基本準則，立即停止插手香港事務及干涉中國內政。"},{"pid":"293b4795ae8aeccf3ef5cfa93e9ee26368754c1d","tid":1436361,"uid":134071,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T09:32:43.000Z","msg":"美國既香港人權法， 應該將華春瑩加入list"},{"pid":"9a1448a4180e93181e948f228772a14aae7fb80f","tid":1436361,"uid":3340,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T09:33:21.000Z","msg":"請美國立刻撤消美國香港關係法<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79d7c166a4448dcb60dccf14889b50a42d0f26a8","tid":1436361,"uid":40628,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T09:33:25.000Z","msg":"人哋美國都計古埋你係貨幣操縱國，你支那仲日日嘴炮<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92ddf7643bcecf91617395d3ea803772ae859cad","tid":1436361,"uid":75959,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"re